{
  "text": "The relationship between the ESP and SAR is given in Fig. 2 based on the data of [CITATION_1] . . Median values of the CCC at each SAR for each type of soil at pH 6.0, 7.5, and 9.0 are represented in Fig. 3, 4 , and 5 for the 8 Ebro Basin, 16 Ramona, and 10 Clarence soils, respectively. These lines rep resent the thresholds between flocculated and dis persed states.",
